org.emocha.model.entities
Class File

java.lang.Object
  org.emocha.model.entities.File

public class File
extends java.lang.Object

File represent a file (either media or form template) which is stored in the sdcard, also has its reference stored in the SQLite database. Files usually are sent from the server to the device.
